Detailed Description

Public class for handling javascript prompt requests.

A JsDialogHandlerInterface implentation will receive a jsPrompt call with a JsPromptResult parameter. This parameter is used to return a result to WebView. The client can call cancel() to cancel the dialog or confirm() with the user's input to confirm the dialog.
